            <title>Change ordinary word (w) to ketiv word (k)</title>
            
            <summary>
                 <note>
                      These words are instances of ketiv without qere in the Masoretic Tanach
                      as indicated in the Masoretic notes.
                      The 8 recognized instances of ketiv without qere are:
